title: 20 MIN HIIT Treadmill Workout
description:
Coach Veronica is back with a 20 Minute HIIT Treadmill Workout!! We are hitting 60 seconds at a base pace before pushing for a minute and doing a 30 second hard push before coming back down to base. Get ready to get sweaty!

20:00 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join our community of runners: http://www.ibxrunning.com
Merch: https://www.ibxrunning.com/store
IBX Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ibxrunning/
Veronica's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bodibyroni/
Rachael's Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bedopefitness/

00:00 - Intro
00:26 - Warm Up
03:24 - Workout!
18:20 - Cool Down

Workout Structure:
WARMUP: 3 minutes 
HIIT SECTION: Repeat 4 times
      BASE PACE: 1 minutes - 5.5 - 7.5 mph
      PUSH PACE: 1 minute - 6.0 - 8.0 mph
      HARD PUSH: 30 seconds - 6.5 - 8.5 mph
RECOVER: 1 minute
LONG PUSH: 4 minutes - 6.0 - 8.0 mph
Cooldown at the end!

Songs Used:
1. Borrowed Matches - Tape Machines
2. I Can Taste Your Words - Ceen
3. New Dawn Is Rising - Stonekeepers
4. Say We're Sorry (Hallman Remix) - Loving Caliber
5. Stick Together (SLCT Remix) - Elijah N
6. Stocked - Damma Beatz
7. We're Out Of Time - Vacancy

What did you enjoy about this workout? What suggestions do you have? We would love to hear from you below 👇
